        <br><span class="ob-hero-hint">Copy to clipboard and paste directly into <code>Obsidian</code>, or download as a file.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="ob-hero-buttons">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg ob-download-btn" id="ob-copy-checklist" onclick="obCopyChecklist()">
        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-copy"></i> COPY TO CLIPBOARD
      </button>
